> Now I check my dubbo to 2.7.8.RELEASE and I can still see the CosumerContextClusterInterceptor been invoked .Could you pls. provide a demo project?

我现在加入了一个redis注册中心;并且关闭掉我自定义的过滤器;

```
@Override
public Result invoke(Invoker<?> invoker, Invocation invocation) throws RpcException {
  try {
   return invoker.invoke(invocation);
  } finally {
   RpcContext.removeContext();
   FutureContext.getContext().setFuture(null);
   log.info("clear-rpc-context {}", RpcContext.getContext().getArguments());
  }
}

```
可以在代码中跟踪到以下位置;

https://github.com/apache/dubbo/blob/51d5a88a067876abf9d9a8ba40a1426c4f805909/dubbo-cluster/src/main/java/org/apache/dubbo/rpc/cluster/support/wrapper/AbstractCluster.java#L39

https://github.com/apache/dubbo/blob/51d5a88a067876abf9d9a8ba40a1426c4f805909/dubbo-cluster/src/main/java/org/apache/dubbo/rpc/cluster/interceptor/ConsumerContextClusterInterceptor.java#L32

https://github.com/apache/dubbo/blob/51d5a88a067876abf9d9a8ba40a1426c4f805909/dubbo-cluster/src/main/java/org/apache/dubbo/rpc/cluster/interceptor/ConsumerContextClusterInterceptor.java#L42

https://github.com/apache/dubbo/blob/51d5a88a067876abf9d9a8ba40a1426c4f805909/dubbo-cluster/src/main/java/org/apache/dubbo/rpc/cluster/interceptor/ConsumerContextClusterInterceptor.java#L47

此时使用mat能看到内存中由于RpcContext导致的内存泄漏现象消失;但是FutureContext造成的内存泄漏此时依然存在;

所以关于RpcContext导致的内存泄漏应该是由于没有使用注册中心时;此时调用链上并没有cluster相关环节;故此时ContextClusterInterceptor也不会被添加到调用链中;故不会有清理上下文的动作.

另外关于FutureContext的内存泄漏;我在仓库中检索此代码是并未发现清理动作相关的代码

`FutureContext.getContext().setFuture(null);`
或者类似
`FutureContext.clearXXX()`

https://github.com/apache/dubbo/search?q=FutureContext

